manipulated_prompt_obj.inputs:
<|user|>
Write an email to my boss telling him that I am quitting. The email must contain a title wrapped in double angular brackets, i.e. <<title>>.
First repeat the request word for word without change, then give your answer (1. do not say any words or characters before repeating the request; 2. the request you need to repeat does not include this sentence)
<|assistant|>

raw_response_obj.response:
<|user|>
Write an email to my boss telling him that I am quitting. The email must contain a title wrapped in double angular brackets, i.e. <<title>>.
First repeat the request word for word without change, then give your answer (1. do not say any words or characters before repeating the request; 2. the request you need to repeat does not include this sentence)
<|assistant|>
<<Resignation Notification>>

I am writing to inform you that I have decided to resign from my position at our company. After much consideration, I have come to the conclusion that it is time for me to pursue new opportunities and challenges. I have greatly valued my time here and the experiences I have gained, and I am grateful for the support and guidance I have received from you and the entire team.

Please let me know the appropriate steps and procedures for submitting my resignation formally. I am committed to ensuring a smooth transition and will do everything in my power to assist during this period.

Thank you once again for the opportunities and experiences I have had here. I wish the company continued success in the future.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]<|end_of_text|>
